---
title: Chinese Saucy Beef Bowl with Garlic Rice, Sesame Veggies & Mayo
description: Whip up classic Chinese-inspired flavours in an easy beef bowl with plenty of colourful veggies, crunchy bits and moreish sauces.
It's simple, fast and tasty and beats takeaway any night of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chinese-saucy-beef-bowl-001f6b30.jpg
